  {
    "hotel_id": "1803429",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/little-beach-hoi-an-a-boutique-hotel-spa/hotel/hoi-an-vn.html",
    "name": "Wyndham Garden Hoi An Cua Dai Beach",
    "detail": "Staying at Little hoi an beach boutique was an a amazing experience from start to finish. The hotel itself is brand new, very luxurious, and rooms are very clean. All of the staff were very kind and took an interest in getting to know us, going out of their way to tell us about local life, things to do in town, and helping us with any request we had. In particular, Joy, Nancy and Susan made us feel very welcome and at home. Breakfast had a very good selection each day and was always fresh. There is a free shuttle service into old town and to the swimming beach which made getting around easy. The only improvement could be more shuttle service times of an evening but cost of a taxi is also very cheap so it was not an issue. Will definitely be coming back to stay next time we are in Hoi An, and would highly recommend the Little hoi an beach boutique to anyone travelling to Hoi An. Thank you Little hoi an beach boutique staff for truly making our stay in hoi an unforgettable!! ",
